  "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/7/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734_2_260x250.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"gV46g6EQghd02PcEdgQ9MM7O17u\" width=\"260\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734_2_260x250.jpeg, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734_2_390x375.jpeg 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734_2_520x500.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"D9E1E8\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2364\u00d71820 228 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/f/fb94d95444690b9c6136e2b6905c5739a736a066.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/fb94d95444690b9c6136e2b6905c5739a736a066\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fb94d95444690b9c6136e2b6905c5739a736a066_2_260x250.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"zTAKEuK1VXgrD3I0wM7sEz9ttf8\" width=\"260\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fb94d95444690b9c6136e2b6905c5739a736a066_2_260x250.jpeg, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fb94d95444690b9c6136e2b6905c5739a736a066_2_390x375.jpeg 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fb94d95444690b9c6136e2b6905c5739a736a066_2_520x500.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"EAEBEB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1584\u00d71520 151 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<aside class=\"onebox githubgist\" data-onebox-src=\"https://gist.github.com/BoltTouring/5376f9cf02b6949252cd17c2f41b453f\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/BoltTouring/5376f9cf02b6949252cd17c2f41b453f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">gist.github.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <h4><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/BoltTouring/5376f9cf02b6949252cd17c2f41b453f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://gist.github.com/BoltTouring/5376f9cf02b6949252cd17c2f41b453f</a></h4>\n\n  <h5>gistfile1.md</h5>\n  <pre><code class=\"Markdown\"># Receiving Silent Payments without scanning\n\n## TL;DR\n\nWe built a complete Silent Payment notification system into [Sparrow Wallet](https://github.com/sparrowwallet/sparrow) using Nostr encrypted DMs. When you send bitcoin to a Nostr identity, the recipient is automatically notified via NIP-17 with everything they need to claim the UTXO \u2014 no blockchain scanning required.\n\nThis is a follow-up to [Part 1](https://gist.github.com/BoltTouring/dde944661df330ec5119af8ef94159e1), which covered sending to Nostr identities. This part covers receiving.\n\n## The Problem\n</code></pre>\n   This file has been truncated. <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/BoltTouring/5376f9cf02b6949252cd17c2f41b453f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">show original</a>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<aside class=\"onebox githubrepo\" data-onebox-src=\"https://github.com/BoltTouring/sparrow\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/BoltTouring/sparrow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">github.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"github-row\" data-github-private-repo=\"false\">\n  <img width=\"690\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5eb8d653b062d30c3dccee8a663c966f7d12f2b3_2_690x344.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"E9E9E8\">\n\n  <h3><a href=\"https://github.com/BoltTouring/sparrow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">GitHub - BoltTouring/sparrow: Desktop Bitcoin Wallet focused on security and...</a></h3>\n\n    <p><span class=\"github-repo-description\">Desktop Bitcoin Wallet focused on security and privacy. Free and open source.</span></p>\n</div>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Archive</summary>\n<aside class=\"onebox discoursetopic\" data-onebox-src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20260314125251/https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/silent-payments-notifications-via-nostr/2203/6\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/1X/863d31b22a9d4d4072777bffb9b9ded86a1638bc.svg\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20260314125251/https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/silent-payments-notifications-via-nostr/2203/6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"12:41PM - 14 March 2026\">Delving Bitcoin \u2013 14 Mar 26</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:649/500;\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/76962e1d35ddc62de32f941d9806c352809cc734_2_649x500.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"649\" height=\"500\" data-dominant-color=\"D9E1E8\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n  <h3><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20260314125251/https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/silent-payments-notifications-via-nostr/2203/6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Silent Payments notifications via Nostr</a></h3>\n  <div class=\"topic-category\">\n      <span class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\">\n        <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color: #F7941D;\"></span>\n        <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\">\n          <span class=\"category-name\">Implementation</span>\n        </span>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\">\n        <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color: #ED207B;\"></span>\n        <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\">\n          <span class=\"category-name\">wg-silent-payments</span>\n        </span>\n      </span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n  <p>This write-up has the goal to discuss the approach of sending notifications for incoming Silent Payments transactions via Nostr.\nThe design is an extension of the discussions around \u201cStealth addresses using nostr\u201d which \u2026</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n</details>",
